MultiChoice has launched a DStv Now app for LG smart TVs. The majority of LG TVs from 2017 and 2018 running webOS 3.5 and 4.0 are supported. The announcement follows the recent launch of DStv Now apps for Samsung smart TVs, Apple TV, and Android TV media players. The company said the new app is available from the LG App Store on supported TVs. To find out how the DStv Now smart TV app works, check out our hands-on with the service.